data.description: OPEN HOUSE this Sunday 11/19 1-3.  Don't miss your opportunity to own a spacious 4 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath home in the sought after neighborhood of Stony Ridge in Reynoldsburg.  Enjoy the oversized deck, mature trees and large fenced in back yard.  Many updates including A/C (2019), roof (2012), hot water heater (2023), new furnace motor (2008), upstairs carpeting (2020), deck painted (2023), all new carpet on st floor 11/(2023),  en-suite bath updated (2020).
